1081\" title=\"minimalism\" src=\"http://weblogtoolscollection.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/minimalism.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"113\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://bestwpblogthemes.com/2012/simple-light-grey-wordpress-theme-simple-minimalism/\"><strong>Minimalism</strong></a> is a very simple minimalist theme with few graphics used.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-11086\" title=\"patchwork\" src=\"http://weblogtoolscollection.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/patchwork.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"113\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://carolinethemes.com/2012/02/21/new-theme-patchwork/\"><strong>Patchwork</strong></a> is a colorful theme with a fun quilted pattern.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-11082\" title=\"sexycity\" src=\"http://weblogtoolscollection.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/sexycity.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"113\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://emptynestthemes.com/2012/02/22/sexy-city-wordpress-theme/\"><strong>Sexy City</strong></a> is dark, rich and eye-catching.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-11083\" title=\"skyhorse\" src=\"http://weblogtoolscollection.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/skyhorse.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"113\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://bestwpblogthemes.com/2012/light-blue-wordpress-theme-sky-horse/\"><strong>Sky Horse</strong></a> is a light blue theme with a good looking sky horse on the header.</p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/weblogtoolscollection/UXMP/~4/_kzSe6W3Ibo\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" />\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sat, 25 Feb 2012 13:00:28 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"James\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_bas